---
layout: "base.njk"
title: Blog
description: "Notes on code, the mind, and the space in between."
image: "/assets/images/cover.jpg"
pagination:
  data: collections
  size: 1
  alias: tag
permalink: /tags/{{ tag }}/
---

<div class="ledger">
  <section class="section">
    <div class="section__index">— writing</div>
    <div class="section__body">
      <h1 class="writing__title">Writing</h1>
      <p class="writing__sub measure">
        Notes on code, the mind, and the space in between. Mostly written to
        think out loud.
      </p>
      <p class="writing__hint">↹ tab through post titles — focused headings show a ring</p>
      {%- include "tags-list.njk" -%}
    </div>
  </section>

  {%- set taglist = collections[tag] -%}
  {%- for blog in taglist | reverse -%}
    {%- include "blog-entry.njk" -%}
  {%- endfor -%}
</div>
